<h1>New Timesheet Entry</h1>

<p>This information will be shown to parents to keep them updated on their studentâ€™s progress.</p>

<%= if @mentee do %>
    <div class="border-radius box-shadow-m padding-m">
        <h2>1. To-Do Lists for <%= @mentee.name %>, Their Parents, and You!</h2>

       What should <%= @mentee.name %> be working on?
       <%= render TznWeb.Mentor.MenteeView,
            "_autosaving_todo_notes.html",
            url: Routes.mentor_mentee_path(@conn, :update, @mentee.id),
            field_name: "mentee_todo_notes",
            initial_html: @mentee.mentee_todo_notes,
            placeholder: "Please use bullet points to create a to-do list. :)"
        %>
        <div class="space-l"></div>

        What can their parent be helping them get done?
        <%= render TznWeb.Mentor.MenteeView,
            "_autosaving_todo_notes.html",
            url: Routes.mentor_mentee_path(@conn, :update, @mentee.id),
            field_name: "parent_todo_notes",
            initial_html: @mentee.parent_todo_notes,
            placeholder: "Please use bullet points to create a to-do list. :)"
        %>

        <div class="space-l"></div>

        What will you be working on for <%= @mentee.name %> outside of meeting times?
        <%= render TznWeb.Mentor.MenteeView,
            "_autosaving_todo_notes.html",
            url: Routes.mentor_mentee_path(@conn, :update, @mentee.id),
            field_name: "mentor_todo_notes",
            initial_html: @mentee.mentor_todo_notes,
            placeholder: "Please use bullet points to create a to-do list. :)"
        %>
    </div>

    <div class="space-l"></div>
<% end %>

<div class="border-radius box-shadow-m padding-m">
    <h2>2. Enter Timesheet Information</h2>
    <%= render "form.html", Map.put(assigns, :action, Routes.mentor_timesheet_entry_path(@conn, :create)) %>
</div>

<div class="space-m"></div>

<%= link "Back to my timesheet", to: Routes.mentor_timesheet_entry_path(@conn, :index) %>

<div class="space-m"></div>
